10 An Act relating to the county planning commission;
amending 19 O.S. 2021, Section 868.2, which relates
11 to the personnel of the county planning commission;
establishing that the chair of the board of county
12 commissioners or their designee shall be a member of
the county planning commission; providing process for
13 appointing remaining members; establishing terms of
two years; amending 19 O.S. 2021, Section 868.3,
14 which relates to personnel and procedure of the
county board of adjustment; requiring the county
15 board of adjustment to be composed of three, five, or
seven appointed resident property owners of the
16 county; providing process for the appointment of
members; establishing terms of members; permitting
17 the board of county commissioners to retain private
legal counsel to represent and advise the county
18 board of adjustment; clarifying certain actions
